  <summary date="2023-08-02T18:04:38Z" status="Introduced in House">VA Caregiver Transparency Act

This bill modifies the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) Program of Comprehensive Assistance for Family Caregivers and Program of General Caregiver Support Services, including by requiring any assistance or support decisions to be subject to the VA's clinical appeals process.</summary>
